settings.description: Head to Boom Boom and fight him as you go through some trouble!
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is the Desert Airship, and transition to water land.

Solve difficult puzzles while keeping Mario on his toes in this icy but warm ghost house.    

Hint: You can carry Flurries when above and on the side of it.
Try and get the mushroom to the end!
este nivel tiene plataformas  y mas
Hurry up, and reach the goal before time runs out!
